title: [Yegharren Valley, Wooded Slope]
description: Acorns lie scattered around the leaf-carpeted soil under a particularly fruitful old oak, and a few red and grey squirrels scamper in and around the tree, gathering their nutty feast even in the night's darkness.  The forest floor dips in a shaded, brush-filled furrow just to the north.
